   - You may NOT use these names for derivative products
   - Use descriptive names like "[YourOrg] Water Monitor (powered by OpenResilience)"

3. DATA SOVEREIGNTY COMMITMENT
   - This software is designed for community data ownership
   - Deployments must respect local data governance
   - Communities must retain control of their data
   - No exploitation of community data for profit

4. ETHICAL USE ONLY
   - May NOT be used for surveillance or oppression
